Dorothea Wolbert https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dorothea_Wolbert 0 Dorothea Wolbert (April 12, 1874 – September 15, 1958) was an American film actress. She appeared in 147 films between 1916 and 1957. She appeared on the television series I Love Lucy (with her character named Dorothea Wolbert) in episode #137, "Ricky's European Booking" (1956). She was born in Philadelphia, Pennsylvania and died in Hollywood, California. Dorothea_Wolbert ( April_12_,_1874 – September_15_,_1958 ) was an_American_film_actress .
